Text:
Gracias papa!!
Saludos de otro boricua.
De nada, Amor borrincano es la que hay!!!1

Muchisimas Gracias! El Gran Combo es mejor todavia. 
Liistening to their joyous music reminds me so of the wonderful times I had when I was privileged to live in Puerto Rico. You cannot listen to this music and sit still.
Again, Many thanks!
